export const projectData = [

    {
        id: 2,
        title: "portfolio architect | React",

            enim. Proin malesuada efficitur convallis. Donec vulputate odio eget semper fringilla.",
        image: [foodDeliveryBackEnd,placeHolder],
        type: 2, // TYPE 2 : FRONT 
        informationPage: {
            componentsImages: [[HomeComponent,Page1Component,Content,ContentCss],
                [Page2,Page2Component,ContentPage2,ContentPage2Css],[MenuBar,MenuBarComponent,MenuBarCss]],
